	    <div class="section-title"> Getting Started </div>

	    <div class="question-title">How do I post a Seed?</div>
	    <div class="answer">From the community view, click the "Add Seed" button from the left hand side of the community toolbar. Follow the instructions on the "Add Seed" form to fill in your details and plant your Seed.</div>

	    <div class="question-title">How do I comment?</div>
	    <div class="answer">From any post, click the comment button to open comments. </div>

	    <div class="question-title">How do I notify other members of my Seed?</div>
	    <div class="answer">There are two ways to accomplish this. The first is to @mention a member in the description of your seed, or in the comments. <br>
	    The second way to accomplish this is to click on the "Add Members" button and enter the member's name in the form.</div>

	    <div class="question-title">How do I add a Topic to my seed?</div>
	    <div class="answer">You can add a topic by typing a # followed by the topic keyword. </div>

	    <div class="question-title">How do I see recent activity?</div>
	    <div class="answer">In the Main Menu (accessed by clicking your community's logo at the top of the screen on desktop, accessed in the hamburger menu on mobile), select "Notifications" to go to a page with all of the recent activity on your Seeds, as well as new comments on Seeds you've joined. </div>

	    <div class="question-title">Who can see my information?</div>
	    <div class="answer">Only the members of your community can see your profile, Seeds or any comments you have made. Members from other communities cannot see your profile or any of your activity. The site is currently in private Beta and none of the content on Hylo is available to the public. </div>
