   		<div class="section-title">Post Features</div>
	   	<div class="question-title">@Mention </div>
	   	<div class="answer">Use this feature to notify other members that you think would be interested in your Seed or could help you spread the word. In the seed description or comments, just type "@" and start writing the person's name. A list will pop up for you to select your collaborators name.</div>

		<div class="question-title">Topics</div>
		 <div class="answer">A Topic allows you to add a searchable keyword to your Seed or comment. Just use the "#" to create #Topics. This makes it easier for people to find things that have a relevant #Topic. For example, if you are looking for a skill, you could type #programming or #writing and if your post is on a specific #Topic, you can type #books or #food.
		@Mentions and #Topics can be used in seed descriptions as well as in comments.</div>

		<div class="question-title">Joining</div>
		<div class="answer">To Join a seed and receive updates, just click the Join button on any Seed. Adding another member to a Seed or @mentioning them in the Seed or comments will also sign them up for updates on the Seed. </div>
	</div>

